definition: (of a smell) strong/peak season (of a crop)/(classifier for the ordinal number of a crop, in the context of multiple harvests)

sentences.english: A test bench for electronic unit pump(EUP) fuel injection system was designed.
sentences.chinese: 设计了电控组合单体泵燃油喷射系统试验台。

sentences.english: They have developed the ability to move rather than just drift, jetting at up to four knots through the water.
sentences.chinese: 它们不止漂浮，还能游动，在水中喷射至四海里。

sentences.english: The jet soared away into the distance.
sentences.chinese: 喷射机不停高飞进入远方。

sentences.english: This aircraft works by jet [ propulsion ].
sentences.chinese: 航空部对喷射推进的兴趣渐浓。

sentences.english: The technique of high-pressure gunite is applied to the foundation anti-seepage and reinforcement engineering and outstanding achievements were acquired.
sentences.chinese: 高压喷射灌浆进行地基防渗加固，取得了显著的成就。

sentences.english: The main task of Electronic Fuel Injection System is to control the fuel injection quantity.
sentences.chinese: 电控燃油喷射系统的主要任务是控制喷油量。

sentences.english: Two-fluid model was employed to simulate two-phase phenomena of supersonic crossflow .
sentences.chinese: 对两相超声速横向喷射试验进行了数值模拟。

sentences.english: The working principle of the two types of ejector is the same .
sentences.chinese: 这两个类型的喷射器工作原理是相同的。

sentences.english: Thirty black beche-de-mer mate, sea cucumbers mate, writhing and squirting.
sentences.chinese: 三十个黑糊糊的海参正在里面蠕动喷射着。

sentences.english: An airplane taxiing down the runway.
sentences.chinese: 我们看着喷射机沿跑道滑行。

sentences.english: That wealthy man has his own jet.
sentences.chinese: 那位富翁拥有自己的喷射机。

sentences.english: The porous nickel was fabricated by using the jet electrodeposition.
sentences.chinese: 采用喷射电沉积方法制备块体多孔镍。

sentences.english: Flamethrowers were used to set houses afire .
sentences.chinese: 火焰喷射手习惯把房屋点燃。

sentences.english: Graphic are good especially when you use the flame thrower.
sentences.chinese: 图形是好的，特别是当您使用火焰喷射器。

sentences.english: Is the water spray system ready for use?
sentences.chinese: 水雾喷射系统是否随时可用？

sentences.english: Probability of blowing up a flamethrower armed soldier is reduced.
sentences.chinese: 降低装备火焰喷射器的士兵爆炸的几率。
